{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.vigramsdk\/documentation\/VigramSDK"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To connect VigramSDK in this example we will use "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/www.swift.org\/package-manager\/","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"We also recommend using this method instead of CocoaPods."}]},{"type":"heading","text":"Step 1. Add Package Dependencies in your project.","anchor":"Step-1-Add-Package-Dependencies-in-your-project","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To add a framework to your project, you need to select Add Package Dependencies in the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"File"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" section of the top menu of Xcode:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"fig1.png"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Paste into the search bar url:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["https:\/\/github.com\/vigram-sw\/SDK_iOS_viDoc_Distribution.git"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"fig2.png"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After entering the address, the SDK name, the current release version, and the project to which the library will be added will appear:"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"fig3.png"}]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Make sure you have access to an internet connection and that the project you are adding the framework to is selected correctly","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Also pay attention to the release version indicated in the window. The version number can be changed manually.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The actual release version is always indicated on the main page of this guide.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"Note","style":"note"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After this, you need to click on the Add Package button:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"fig4.png"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"After this, the process of checking and unpacking the library will begin. Wait until it is finished:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"fig5.png"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Select your project:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"fig6.png"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Once you add the project, the dependency will appear in the "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Package Dependencies","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" section of your project. Again, pay attention to the library version:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"fig7.png"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Try building the project. To do this, select the Build command in the "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Product"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":" section or run the command using hotkeys ("},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"command + b","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":")"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"fig8.png"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the project builds successfully, all actions have been performed correctly."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Step-2-Import-library","text":"Step 2. Import library","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"To use VigramSDK tools you need to import framework into your class:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["import VigramSDK"],"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"fig9.png"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This completes the framework import procedure."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The next step is ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"overridingTitle":"to authenticate the SDK.","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"text":"to authenticate the SDK.","type":"text"}],"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vigramsdk\/documentation\/VigramSDK\/Step2SDKAuthentication"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"*All methods and functions specified in this manual are also available in the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/vigram-sw\/SDK_iOS_viDoc_Distribution\/tree\/demo\/","isActive":true}]},{"text":"Navigation","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Navigation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"text":"Up to Getting started with VigramSDK","type":"text"}],"overridingTitle":"Up to Getting started with VigramSDK","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vigramsdk\/documentation\/VigramSDK\/GettingStarted"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"✅ ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"STEP 1 (Import VigramSDK)"}],"type":"strong"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"overridingTitle":"STEP 2 (SDK Authentication)","type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vigramsdk\/documentation\/VigramSDK\/Step2SDKAuthentication","isActive":true,"overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"STEP 2 (SDK Authentication)"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.vigramsdk\/documentation\/VigramSDK\/Step3ConfigurationParameters","overridingTitle":"STEP 3 (Description of configuration parameters)","isActive":true,"type":"reference","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"STEP 3 (Description of conf